  Home_Energy,
  Home_Accessories,
  Home_Weekly,
  Home_Statistics,
  Home_Join,
  Fadein,
} from "../comps/Portal";

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Fadein>
        <Hero />
      </Fadein>
      <Fadein>
        <Home_Statistics />
      </Fadein>
      <Fadein>
        <Home_Vehicles />
      </Fadein>
      <Fadein>
        <Home_Planet />
      </Fadein>
      <Fadein>
        <Home_Energy />
      </Fadein>
      <Fadein>
        <Home_Accessories />
      </Fadein>

      <Fadein>
        <Home_Weekly />
      </Fadein>
      <Home_Join />
    </>
  );
};

export default Home;
